# Tools that travel to every project (both .ps1/.sh twins per name).
# Consumed by: new-project.{ps1,sh} (scaffold) and propagate-tools.{ps1,sh} (update
# existing projects). Kit-only scripts (new-project, check-kit-docs, propagate-tools)
# and gate.template.* (copied as gate.* by the scaffolder) are NOT listed.
# One base name per line; '#' starts a comment.
verify-path-health
sync-repo
checkpoint
rescue
report-snag
launch-claude-clean
verify-file-integrity
check-git-identity
install-hooks
check-reference-coverage
new-reference-page
release-notes
test-hostile-env
safe-agent-push
